pullRequest.title: Fix chunk is loaded condition
pullRequest.bodyText:
Description
This PR aims to fix an issue with the is chunk loaded condition.
The main issue is when grabbing a chunk object (ie: chunk at location) the chunk is therefor loaded, and this condition will always return true.

Target Minecraft Versions: any
Requirements: none
Related Issues: #2716
